BYNUM
v.
PROGRESSIVE INS. GROUP, INC., et al. No. 338P14-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Nov. 5, 2015. Waddell Bynum, Charlotte, for Bynum, Waddell.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 21st of September 2015 by Plaintiff to Appeal:

"Motion Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of November 2015."
